PrecisRegulations Amending the CANADA GRAIN REGULATIONS which reduce the fee for the official weighing of grain on inward railcars, truckloads and containers at terminal elevators, inland terminal elevators and transfer elevators, from $14.75 per carload to $5.90 per carload, effective April 1, 1998.
